-- Mauritius Statistics Office Cuts Economic-Growth Forecast to 4.1% for 2010
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2010-09-30T06:18:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/mauritius-statistics-office-cuts-economic-growth-forecast-to-4-1-for-2010.html
Mauritius lowered its economic-
growth forecast for 2010 to 4.1 percent from 4.2 percent,
according to a statement published on the website of the Port
Louis-based Central Statistics Office today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  